ARMED thugs attacked and robbed Debonairs Pizza in
Keningston, Joburg. In the video, two armed thugs are seen ordering customers
to go in the back of the store. While one of the thugs escorts the customers, the one
thug that is left behind is seen instructing a store manager to open the tills. The thugs are then seen pocketing cash from the tills. Debonairs Pizza tweeted: "We are saddened that our
customers and staff had to endure this robbery. We are doing what we can to
support them and assist the police in the pursuit of justice." 